The paper proposes a new formulation for SVM regression problems that incorporates additional data samples or Universum. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it deals with developing a new learning algorithm. Additionally, the paper incorporates a priori knowledge in the form of additional data samples, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Vision (cs.CV). The empirical comparisons presented in the paper suggest that it may also belong to the sub-categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
